summary: Adds 2 cabbages in a bucket, convienantly placed in Riverwood.
descriptionHtml:
Adds 2 cabbages in a bucket, convienantly placed in Riverwood in response to the thread: "Petition to restitute the Mod "Cabbage in A Pot" on the Nexus" http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/948087-petition-to-restitute-the-mod-cabbage-in-a-pot-on-the-nexus/

I know I cannot replace the Cabbage in a pot, but I can bring forth 2 cabbages 1 bucket!

This mod is meant as is, for humor purposes only. But I hear the cabbages are good to make cabbage soup.

Just for fun I hid them someplace in Whiterun. Find em if you can!

[spoiler]
